Reference

Table Queries

Main functions for querying the CAX HLI database.

rcax_nosa()

Get nosa table for a popid

rcax_escdata()

Get EscData table

rcax_superpops()

Get SuperPopulations table

rcax_tables()

Get the list of CAX tables with ids

rcax_table_query()

Returns a filtered table or colnames

Connecting to API

Functions for connecting to the API. These are for internal and developers use.

rcax_GET()

Make a GET call to API

rcax_base()

Set the base API url

rcax_ua()

Make the user agent string

rcax_key()

Print message re how to get CAX API key

check_key()

Get the key from the user system environment variable

rcax_parse()

Parse results from API call

rcax_filter()

Create filter to add to GET call
